===Noun===
'''weaning'''

# {{italbrac|[[gerund]]}} The (passive) process of a child or animal ceasing to be dependant on the mother for nourishment.

===Related expression===
#(to) be weaned: a child is considered "[[weaned]]" as soon as it does not receive breast milk any longer and can rely on solid food.

